
The mailbox_size.pl is a perl program that get information in the the mail account table.

The program get email and maildir folder, and get the maildir folder size to store
it in a another database.

With this program we can follow user disk usage, this his usefull to know if we have
to ask a customer if he need more space or not.

Requirement :

Perl
DBI : Mysql
Mysql
Maildir folder has mail storage 

Tested on a FreeBSD System but should work on any Unix.

